{"tid":92342,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[不想放大只想放大被放大] 黑房日記","createTime":"2017-01-23T13:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T10:32:13.000Z","uid":18111,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2b997dd78f42949006d69b3816692eef0570c4","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"話說玩左好耐菲林, 黑白又玩左好一段日子. 上年年中去左次終環克店黑房放相體驗班(個到真是體驗only, d 設備麻麻, 玩下無妨)。 之後又科多次水租幾個鐘曬下自己D相, 但是時間真是好有限, 曬出泥唔滿意, 想再執又要再Book過。(個到D野又一般般) 因此, 決定要自己setup間黑房! 故事就是咁開始. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前是克店放既相. <br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/xm2vlzSSHGnvUi34NMvy8VcOwI7GLKCG08JgTlYr5GMKGI4sHXVTFWZXiKgrJ2S1bv_fDB35pQaQ3Qr7rUQJg6iNUsnli5ZLpxAb8PxodiSzGshIzIuWjTiSPjo0cXg62wOB00O8LRPMcKkXU6oRR32WOqnBrt69gOOYeI0lzWB3Zg4xybBtPEE1SW0gYU-aKTT7kOUCTU-Ptln8_6YtS77u-sZkWV2Wn-m7QUHx_vWxyQLZGHGzWOft8mQ7PK3ieTG5csK_hmGR0Vyt87HVUDumD3xTy-zWrbLwg2Hz8wMEijKKEunWSmrlfh2BXvX6HGIr0yuvWDC9xI4UoP5e-OxEaEOLzLKxv5yFYkLqlFU5KpMlrRVF3sA_zjbObokat7x2tZlk1RDrY-HJucwu9OVqlDKm8YuF1FpAOJpWS2V7TiY-kfIIFiMdXB0KysW58JzHoUeXwf8RJNwlC12gdVpAPETeNPwBBqBOBECOi0ruVe7PEsex-wKRL-XjwQ0ltMvssh-IikIBGeeuCEjCDoNKsbMMVxIi_AzNXZG7ORfg_joBFnry_YNGmkkExmpDE5RxByRwuBa6WUFyyZMp3hfUaBqUy0FUOlNNlBH60bbQqM8-7EgDAoPglnBw7cU5VvlD7oUL-REz4azGPOhP902iaE3cxE0CA6pW8QexWA=w1427-h1070-no?.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fxm2vlzSSHGnvUi34NMvy8VcOwI7GLKCG08JgTlYr5GMKGI4sHXVTFWZXiKgrJ2S1bv_fDB35pQaQ3Qr7rUQJg6iNUsnli5ZLpxAb8PxodiSzGshIzIuWjTiSPjo0cXg62wOB00O8LRPMcKkXU6oRR32WOqnBrt69gOOYeI0lzWB3Zg4xybBtPEE1SW0gYU-aKTT7kOUCTU-Ptln8_6YtS77u-sZkWV2Wn-m7QUHx_vWxyQLZGHGzWOft8mQ7PK3ieTG5csK_hmGR0Vyt87HVUDumD3xTy-zWrbLwg2Hz8wMEijKKEunWSmrlfh2BXvX6HGIr0yuvWDC9xI4UoP5e-OxEaEOLzLKxv5yFYkLqlFU5KpMlrRVF3sA_zjbObokat7x2tZlk1RDrY-HJucwu9OVqlDKm8YuF1FpAOJpWS2V7TiY-kfIIFiMdXB0KysW58JzHoUeXwf8RJNwlC12gdVpAPETeNPwBBqBOBECOi0ruVe7PEsex-wKRL-XjwQ0ltMvssh-IikIBGeeuCEjCDoNKsbMMVxIi_AzNXZG7ORfg_joBFnry_YNGmkkExmpDE5RxByRwuBa6WUFyyZMp3hfUaBqUy0FUOlNNlBH60bbQqM8-7EgDAoPglnBw7cU5VvlD7oUL-REz4azGPOhP902iaE3cxE0CA6pW8QexWA%3Dw1427-h1070-no%3F.jpg%20&h=71a615a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己都玩左好一陣子攝影, 乜都影, 乜都玩. 是影相方便都有少少得著。諗諗下還點間黑房由零開始, 不如就開個Post, 分享下, 交個朋友, 海納百川, 聽下意見, 又導多D人一齊玩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好.<br />\n<br />\n首先要了解下 放相(曬相) 是咩一回事. 道理其實好簡單, 就是 放大張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. 叫 曬相 是因為要放大張相 是需要用燈光照過張底片(菲林), 將個投影 曬落張相紙到. 所以, 說透了, 放相同曬相是同一樣野泥。<br />\n<br />\n沖曬 沖曬, 其實是講緊兩樣 &ndash; 沖菲林+ 曬相。 有D人叫沖相, 其實是同沖菲林混淆左.<br />\n<br />\n簡單易明如下:<br />\n<br />\n影相&gt; 沖菲林 &gt; 㨂番張想放大既底片&gt; 放相.<br />\n<br />\n另外, 沖菲林是要無光, 但唔需要黑房, 放相都要無光, 但就一定要黑房lu.<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳, 講番自己要整黑房.<br />\n<br />\n由於黑房都要一D器材, 所以整左個checklist<br />\n<br />\n放大機 _______________買左, 未到<br />\n放相尺板_______________OK<br />\n放大機時計_______________未買<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭_______________OK<br />\n安全燈_______________未買<br />\nMultigrade Filter _______________OK<br />\n盤_______________未買<br />\n夾_______________未買<br />\n刮水夾_______________好似有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藥水_______________未買<br />\n相紙_______________OK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先, 再Update <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67afb48a61a5e22b31146a51990cc7e34db99c19","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:51:56.000Z","msg":"影d 買左既野先<br />\n兩支富士龍放大鏡頭 50mm 是比135底用, 75mm比120底用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgHL573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgHL573.jpg&h=95c5049f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/23/215137_546e692c118e7481d463fd671afbd49b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2F215137_546e692c118e7481d463fd671afbd49b.jpg&h=d02cf605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6W1O6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6W1O6h.jpg&h=403a8f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/436t01Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F436t01Y.jpg&h=f348f247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a617c01b14b145238ecdd8e785bb53019899501","tid":92342,"uid":62971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9596cf90dab2d28c538f7d0369d3ff7f9286c957","tid":92342,"uid":38233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e68f4aca4eb9cc1e3ae48f4df82e9f62f0b6133","tid":92342,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"藝術家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4791b525e3d7e8ccac9a91acaad05dd1071059b4","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:25:16.000Z","msg":"部機到左, 都幾大部.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6877DVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6877DVF.jpg&h=43db50c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上檯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/132455_26bd809c99b16c3d026f623e96c294f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F132455_26bd809c99b16c3d026f623e96c294f0.jpg&h=06c4c1b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b044da08fb611466142742160c695094679568d5","tid":92342,"uid":14885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"巴打係自己房放相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe419d04fc1d2da4b7fc4f9a277435ac4837a2dd","tid":92342,"uid":34242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"準焦放大鏡<br />\n乾燥機"},{"pid":"8dc0b200dd6afdf4ae0e2bb8c22b478dba879593","tid":92342,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"留名跟大師學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b32e734dd635f49451a5d75c8b5c098e054be7","tid":92342,"uid":39355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"仲諗住巴打係出面有地方,想去參觀,點知係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOFFTOPIC 一問,我以前有用開老豆部單反菲琳機影相,基本操作都識,但之後好耐無掂,近派拎返部機發現換左電個快門都卡下卡下,<br />\n阿爸拎去鋪頭比人睇人地都唔肯整,依家有少少時間玩,想買過部,但對相機真係零認識,驚買左返黎又係壞/有問題, 巴打有無邊間鋪頭/相機型號可以提供下? 麻煩哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131ad6fc96b8681b92f29199a61ec1e5fd87eb56","tid":92342,"uid":54663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"新手得部lomography，留名學嘢"},{"pid":"0ac1d360b111bbc7e419c5c178e9bf68f8dd85f5","tid":92342,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"彩放機點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d573a2d9c39c9c01a6b4d165557d4f7e50cc760","tid":92342,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:51:04.000Z","msg":"留名睇痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556695b5290161fd3b7ea5d4f5877981c52838dc","tid":92342,"uid":2331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"試過曬相之後就好想成日去曬相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ea07d1c2c0452fca0048644c4b7e10b28ba57b","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係自己房放相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99ae4b3575f5f33710881e06506e9baebf4fccc","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準焦放大鏡<br />\n乾燥機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部機有個好得意既功能, 可以用個film holder 對焦, 原理有d 似旁軸相機. 型號是Meopta Maginfax 3a<br />\n<br />\n不過長遠都應該會買番個準焦鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整乾d紙 又是一個問題, 依家迴避緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗著釣乾先"},{"pid":"ed93d64b807d089ffb0b8fe5fa0c5d1b9569e95a","tid":92342,"uid":18111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住巴打係出面有地方,想去參觀,點知係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOFFTOPIC 一問,我以前有用開老豆部單反菲琳機影相,基本操作都識,但之後好耐無掂,近派拎返部機發現換左電個快門都卡下卡下,<br />\n阿爸拎去鋪頭比人睇人地都唔肯整,依家有少少時間玩,想買過部,但對相機真係零認識,驚買左返黎又係壞/有問題, 巴打有無邊間鋪頭/相機型號可以提供下? 麻煩哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港普遍貴d, 平dd 狀態又唔是太好, 新手好易比人水/睇漏眼.<br />\n<br />\n我自己多是ebay 買寄去屋企, 用paypal 比錢唔是好難. 香港我建議dcfever 二手區睇下. <br />\n<br />\n型號都是Nikon FM 系. Olympus 個d OM 都幾正, 平d, 又細部d. Canon F 之類."},{"pid":"e68ea3dbf935ac9a33c7cad0f98bf14566fa682d","tid":92342,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>準焦放大鏡<br />\n乾燥機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部機有個好得意既功能, 可以用個film holder 對焦, 原理有d 似旁軸相機. 型號是Meopta Maginfax 3a<br />\n<br />\n不過長遠都應該會買番個準焦鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整乾d紙 又是一個問題, 依家迴避緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗著釣乾先</blockquote><br />\n相紙會有水跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0908c2a6e17304652d32e7db63ba4b1ecf0c57b9","tid":92342,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"留名 有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6154468cda8f905893d8acc5ff95df1df356ed","tid":92342,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"黎緊應該都會同幾個朋友夾份整一間<br />\n請問你d野係邊度買<br />\nebay定點?"},{"pid":"59cbdc65a48d315775414320da15d21f86cf8212","tid":92342,"uid":43527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"痴孖筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2877abdc97d46621fba28e94e0e4cb5a83f5bbdd","tid":92342,"uid":74358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"afe364770cfaf6727bd4beb0eba804eca850c4c0","tid":92342,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:07:01.000Z","msg":"犀利<br />\n推"},{"pid":"5d2ccb84844b54093dbbba72241fb7520a1e26f8","tid":92342,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>準焦放大鏡<br />\n乾燥機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部機有個好得意既功能, 可以用個film holder 對焦, 原理有d 似旁軸相機. 型號是Meopta Maginfax 3a<br />\n<br />\n不過長遠都應該會買番個準焦鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整乾d紙 又是一個問題, 依家迴避緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗著釣乾先</blockquote><br />\n相紙會有水跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nphotoflo + 水夾"},{"pid":"7679977d3fcef9dc95bfa3a641e1de393ee75505","tid":92342,"uid":271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:10:07.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}